  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Capacity Building for VHAI Team and Partners</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The three-year partnership with VHAI will enable Heifer India to train VHAI&apos;s team and partners in the Heifer sustainable Values-Based Holistic Community Development model, including hosting exchange visits to Heifer project sites.  VHAI will host Heifer IN at its meetings and also provide office space for the Heifer IN team in its facility, which will give Heifer India a strong base from which to begin operations.  Heifer India (Heifer IN) and the Voluntary Health Association of India (VHAI) will conduct roundtable discussions to learn together and share experiences and knowledge.</narrative>
  </description>
